Class AFFieldInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tomscz.afrest.rest.dto.AFFieldInfo

    java.io.Serializable

    public class AFFieldInfo
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class store all information about concrete field. Including settings and validations. It can perform any action with component, because it is only component definition.
